OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes dismissal of
OL,4,Clegal challenge to Irish language
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FStormont's First Minister has welcomed
OL,8,Fa judge's dismissal of a legal
OL,9,Fchallenge against Belfast City
OL,10,FCouncil's draft Irish language policy.
OL,12,FThe case against the proposal was
OL,13,Ftaken by TUV member Ann McClure who
OL,14,Fargued the council had not followed
OL,15,Fguidelines on protecting minority
OL,16,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
