CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776877554
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes dismissal of
OL,4,Clegal challenge to Irish language
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FThe policy aims to promote the Irish
OL,8,Flanguage, including interpreting and
OL,9,Ftranslation of key documents and
OL,10,Fpublications, as well as the use of
OL,11,FIrish on the council website, signage
OL,12,Fand council logo.
OL,14,FLanguage policies at a Stormont level
OL,15,Fcome under the remit of DUP
OL,16,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons.
OL,18,FMichelle O'Neill told reporters on
OL,19,FTuesday: "I very much welcome the
OL,20,Fcourt decision this morning.
OL,26,@{D@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776877554
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes dismissal of
OL,4,Clegal challenge to Irish language
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,F"I only saw the headlines of it
OL,8,Fbecause we've been at this event, but
OL,9,FI very much welcome the fact that it
OL,10,Fhas now been dismissed, and the
OL,11,Fminister now needs to get on and
OL,12,Fdeliver an Irish language strategy,
OL,13,Fbecause the Irish language is
OL,14,Fthriving, it's vibrant, it's exciting.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
