OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes dismissal of
OL,4,Clegal challenge to Irish language
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FIf those concerns are upheld, an 80%
OL,8,Fsupermajority may be required to
OL,9,Freapprove the decision.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Belfast City Council
OL,12,Fwelcomed the judgment and said they
OL,13,Fhad "successfully defended the main
OL,14,Fgrounds of challenge and the court
OL,15,Ffound that our current standing orders
OL,16,Fare lawful".
OL,26,@uD@EOUxD@KO]
