OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes dismissal of
OL,4,Clegal challenge to Irish language
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,F"The call-in received in relation to
OL,8,Fthe council's Irish language policy,
OL,9,Ffrom October 2025, is still to be
OL,10,Fconsidered. We have not yet received
OL,11,Fthis legal opinion," they said.
